{"tid":436791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道我說的每一句都是反話嗎?","createTime":"2017-10-15T12:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T18:08:59.000Z","uid":153992,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"98cdcfc50db0d134c587849334c8de722ef6459f","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"我地已經有一段時間冇聯絡<br />\n對上一次同你對話 我同你講 我地唔會再有機會一齊 我好憎你<br />\n呢一世都唔想見到你<br />\n而我相信你都覺得我好憎你<br />\n但你知道我講既每一句都係反話嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n只不過係 我唔可以唔咁講<br />\n因為你已經有下一任了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同我講話你仲鐘意我<br />\n但事實上就算係真 你都同時愛緊你現任吧<br />\n我唔想打擾你地<br />\n亦唔想比你覺得我仲好在意<br />\n<br />\n現在既你 好似好幸福<br />\n比起同我一齊既時候 更幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者佢比我更適合你<br />\n所以我知道已經回不去了<br />\n就算幾掛住幾掛住都好<br />\n我現在只能做既就係強迫自己去忘記<br />\n又或者其實你一早已經唔在意了<br />\n剩低我自己一個仲係原點徘徊 就係似個傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈左係個心到好耐 唔知可以係邊到發洩<br />\n歡迎大家鬧醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abdfab726e25501eec91d841b546cd7f7cb8630","tid":436791,"uid":17306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"點解要講反話？"},{"pid":"e36b8b6c81f0ca4817b3ecbed8e2dab4be78cca3","tid":436791,"uid":152934,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"你知道我說的每一句都是反話嗎?<br />\n<br />\nThis 是唔是反話？"},{"pid":"adc027839ca9b2564eacf447dfa67cadf9852959","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要講反話？</blockquote><br />\n因為我知我地已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n乾脆舉慧劍 斷情絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbf87dca38db3a826560c7655f7b7e8730f0765","tid":436791,"uid":73859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"原來有同路人"},{"pid":"e509518aa00d97deb20fc65d6960c6777e4a01eb","tid":436791,"uid":116792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"其實可以點樣有效分辯到女仔係講緊反話<br />\n定係心底話<br />\n特別係分手嗰啲其間"},{"pid":"04fac36fa31bb833e3fcf400cb10ff04aab1aab1","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來有同路人</blockquote><br />\n你係點?"},{"pid":"bda88bbc2de01aa83f4afd2beac8d5d1f4b3ded2","tid":436791,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"真係鍾意你就唔會唔氹返你<br />\n佢都有新仔/女 話仲鍾意你都係呃你架啫"},{"pid":"f46011215bf7713c2caa1b791134010dc5cbd4da","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係鍾意你就唔會唔氹返你<br />\n佢都有新仔/女 話仲鍾意你都係呃你架啫</blockquote><br />\n認同 個心仲有你既話 又點會捨得同第二個一齊"},{"pid":"3dcbe92adad722c03ea0a9a5b8e826b5179a5476","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以點樣有效分辯到女仔係講緊反話<br />\n定係心底話<br />\n特別係分手嗰啲其間</blockquote><br />\n冇得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只能話你仲鐘意既就努力吧<br />\n佢都鐘意既就自然會返黎你身邊"},{"pid":"40a2181e5b0d3c5ea66371813ae51d9994b5c9c3","tid":436791,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"都冇咩所謂了"},{"pid":"cf8f8e48c247a8ec1fe7be0b98cb26a7181d8310","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都冇咩所謂了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772bece50e3025b89156fbebe78ce3b647760e03","tid":436791,"uid":150595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"你GE感受只有你一個人在意<br />\n喜怒哀樂<br />\n<br />\n點解對自己咁殘忍?<br />\n<br />\n呢樣O野我十歲果時已經知"},{"pid":"2655f587e488bdadce4746f602cd89e8432ea6f2","tid":436791,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你GE感受只有你一個人在意<br />\n喜怒哀樂<br />\n<br />\n點解對自己咁殘忍?<br />\n<br />\n呢樣O野我十歲果時已經知</blockquote><br />\n有時無果種身分，<br />\n講乜都冇資格，<br />\n咪做盡相反嘅事講相反嘅話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce016a96317e33ee4f071d7058d137b435381c64","tid":436791,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都冇咩所謂了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講反話，<br />\n而你相信了，<br />\n我還要裝著不在乎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cead49d447bb62e2801246d67be96db86213d12","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你GE感受只有你一個人在意<br />\n喜怒哀樂<br />\n<br />\n點解對自己咁殘忍?<br />\n<br />\n呢樣O野我十歲果時已經知</blockquote><br />\n其實係 我學識既係以後做決定以自己感受行先<br />\n因為人地都係會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea332e091f1804538908591c6f6bf3b46712e900","tid":436791,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:01:27.000Z","msg":"相反 我係現任但發現佢同ex仲有一齊出街仲要拖住手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ed9b829fa012942fcaf30cf7c929eabb0a38bc","tid":436791,"uid":153797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T00:03:24.000Z","msg":"不歡而散<br />\n<br />\n好　終於都不歡散去　真想不到我會這麼狠　叫你　對我　永遠也死心<br />\n走　今生不想再見你　應該只得這最差的人　只會　對你使出這種口吻<br />\n<br />\n如果分手沒痛楚　<br />\n我怕你　到永遠　也會等我<br />\n如果今天起憎我　仇恨我　歧視我　<br />\n明日你會更易再愛人<br />\n平伏這個美麗心魔　餘生可以好好過<br />\n如果忍不住痛楚　<br />\n當我錯　當我錯　會更好過<br />\n如果必須想起我　<br />\n仇恨我　歧視我　懷念過去快樂太折磨<br />\n無謂美化昨日戀歌　<br />\n拿報復者的決心　活得好更多"},{"pid":"e669dea41d377c38bf4b3c0090c5b6814158ea55","tid":436791,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9d6840a05cacdda6f595e7c9e4858a14ad6198d","tid":436791,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知道我說的每一句都是反話嗎?<br />\n<br />\nThis 是唔是反話？</blockquote><br />\n是"},{"pid":"73df828d4c584ce058937d6231c240f767bd98cf","tid":436791,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵撚死 你自己攞黎<br />\n講d咁既野hurt完人仲想扮受害者 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n啱"},{"pid":"4d112a313aa19a11c6c97083aab991479a36bfd2","tid":436791,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"想喊就喊出黎"},{"pid":"0f3c3246f5d434914519babb1ae606562ada619e","tid":436791,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"點解你咁蠢拆穿唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e541e8da2572d618276856e4a4c18034f5a494c2","tid":436791,"uid":153992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你咁蠢拆穿唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢已經冇諗吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20962bd7024e94d0afd5129eefa9f0ec8e46a116","tid":436791,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}